<li><a href="http://manual.macromates.com/en/working_with_text#column_selections">Column Selections</a> and <a href="http://manual.macromates.com/en/working_with_text#column_movement_typing">Column Typing</a></li>
<li><a href="http://manual.macromates.com/en/working_with_text#completion">Completion of Words from Current Document</a></li>
